<title>自行车房车，还是第一次看到，惊倒一片！</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KadX5rbQHj</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KadX5rbQHj</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;一人，一房车，一狗，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;开着房车看世界，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;四海为家，边走边看，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这是多少人梦寐以求的事情。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6666666666666666&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIFRQSt6hmFKCF00bibz0jqmEM85tFKW1YQArpNicTnwC7rbG2nN0xgiaog/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;然而很多人了解到房车价格后，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;对这样的旅行也只能望而却步。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;不过这些事情怎么能难倒国外的高手们，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;爆改自行车、三轮车、大货车，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;脑洞大到让人惊掉下巴！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6640625&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIibbFewgfr392aLUmu4Yx3HgOrRokVrr3zUDx0jjdfbFQOJVib35MCTrQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;爆改三轮车&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这种车在我国乡村遍地都是，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;谁能想到老外要开着它去旅行！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;3.1035714285714286&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIeDlxZh6ghBJ4RZcqgYSoNL7QicMJf7x39N5gv4AIZmQaYlZiaXLCtQUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;卧室、厨房、储物柜，应有尽有，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;麻雀虽小，五脏俱全！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;加个“屋顶”还能扩容~&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.5&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIJPyTg4vPcciayCWFEzEcL6tGVgDJaLxMyVYNYD2QpIHXpLw2ZrQ5pGg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;各式各样外形的三轮房车&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图纸在了，任凭大家各自发挥自己的想象力了！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.393092105263158&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIb78WZgY0ZqOyORJiaxowib6WzR515SQU3akScuXzrre3NSlNHFHp4RnQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;608&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2482142857142857&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIAeJUdrC4CSoLVDtnXu4KbOMsQnVYn5LibLErPndmeic61Z2g7wuGsiaqA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这个就简单粗暴了，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;只有一张床哈哈哈哈哈哈&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;吃饭的时候要驾出一个小平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;2.3421985815602837&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIqZX7y6jCaib0UHs9gN46XEcr7RpWw0xLXB4Fuj7m88sOHcasDlHOAvw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;刷个好看的漆就是一个小清新&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6666666666666666&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIG8ObeVOxosAIyw7TFbRZUcichYx5Cic8tvZL5cMAAMib1icHb1BTLP4DwQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;除了后厢式的，还有拖挂式的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;外观像一个小面包，更加小巧&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但也只能当做睡觉的场所啦&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2839285714285715&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyI5HT0BCb36s5VicMpEfDNYmBHQLCQTALg8fbLWibPVIkIQQGUaqAz8cEA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIEwzkicwTlycEkKgiawPrf0TYMDC0o1w9YzVjiclwrxWUWq7oEfosx7h9Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIF0SVFzfObf1o2v2hEZz6UDUdibribc9ttcJjUnxOmMkauxCYs6DM63wg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;564px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;是不是有种小花轿的感觉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;开到森林的花丛中，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;邀一位佳人共度下午茶。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6648936170212766&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyI5CCsZACcC6edicr0zbViakg2r8H3s8gtsicskQyrDdOpcVggURYy5Oqaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4326241134751773&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIgABQPksLMqEI26XYIK9rxUyOq3VAiabibkm4lma11MVrV9J7hQVhJcyQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;懒人担心载不动？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;不用担心还有电动房车啊&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;应该很耗电吧&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9946428571428572&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyI0k4CC1tA0hB9AGNaVpBWJwUvgA3ia8tbmWVicMFib6fhYJA4oIv0RosxQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyInJZzWNicGldgUick1EXBibB8iaQ69RIAKYJgl2xgDiaEicR10ZP7plCn8Few/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这应该算是升级豪华版了&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;马力十足&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5709219858156028&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIG6P3eFP1Wff5QLR4SNSz2C74dkwNDhkpqRXaSYZLB59GH8eFpEHLBA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8067375886524822&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyILaic3oKW8prY5vHmH7m46Avz5vfzS7j6nBiaj7k0yGC97rS10sibdBXFg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;还有摩托房车，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;带你装X带你飞！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.0017857142857143&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIpPpTlLpWPYMAqVSh6HYBeMuSaMn9YLJIib85YssJnkxpCA16WUzP9GA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;除了托在身后，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;还可以加几个轮子放在一侧&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIzRmsRCkwohBFa8q7AsIQrA0CJNbLB7BsZkUiapJibNce2XUnEXI6XLJQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;梦想者改造的房车，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;就是一个行走的移动城堡！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;span&gt;是不是很拉风？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIONQQBz9OibOkDWRLN8g1uffOnxtHULLaKczNY2ic9QHrSVSQIzVlCrDA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;500&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/VQVq58maiaPP3dJEzBojBxJicuVPm2eICcXqLCCoTIWWFAicFRjz44efTsoEph9WX5OXib7UVZ9DiaWib3JsfhZrSiadQ/640?&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;560&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;968.4587813620071&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;1715.1254480286736&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.3339285714285714&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyImRyiagEDwBslNAB8pnw1aQmibWYHRH6rbaWRia5yBfztGchTTnRb0SEjA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;560&quot; width=&quot;558px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;对比了那么多自行、摩托房车，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;或者房车真的很豪华了！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;再加上彩绘艺术，酷到飞起！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyIC33WZicoVYgJRQx0ZvSqU2uYIM6yEfb2dOHur3klx0mxnN337T9YHUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;500&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;而且货车改装的容量还超大&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;两室一厅，妥妥滴！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7775&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyISmsGzhngNUZibibgGEibick18PicfOkpum0iaibTdV57sD8xWqXX2xDpWNl1A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;400&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;各式各样的软装，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;也是豪华的大户人家了！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;2.024822695035461&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feuwMtiavgsiauGfiaiayCFVNNdLGhJ4gCyILBJnkdCo4iaks55mbEJGMOjFNJgeiclB1hckZV6TU52DwLwaMZR6YEwQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;564&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

